Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的修行還遠遠不夠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要往這邊去了  再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  回見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女性公敵  放棄抵抗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊  櫻井？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這個人到底做了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都暈過去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對罪犯不需要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不  我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}勞駕{\r}\NExcuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,White is...pen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}新幹線要怎麼乘坐{\r}\NHow can I take a Shinkansen？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}有什麼特別的事情需要我做嗎{\r}\NIs there anything special I have to do？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…是說到了新幹線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}要搭乘新幹線的話{\r}\NTo take a Shinkansen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}你需要新幹線特急券和普通乘車券各一張{\r}\NYou need limited express ticket and a normal one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}如果你需要幫助  可以去找售票處{\r}\NIf you need some help, there is a ticket office over there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海  多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英語什麼的  給我好好學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為鐵道腦的妨礙  我記不住英語單詞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懲處罪犯還要寫檢討  難以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別用鉛筆  用原子筆寫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能重寫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼連這麼瑣碎的事情都得寫上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你吧  把那個給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  我才不想輸給男生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  為什麼還把人給搞暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制伏住他不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打暈他不是更方便處理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是反而麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偶爾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵  有什麼我可以幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  不過不要緊  我一個人搞的定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把字寫錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三行的「待」寫成了「侍」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是些啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看名字根本想像不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是魚肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚼勁不錯的  一入口會讓人以為是肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠶豆湯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地中海一帶還是挺常見的菜式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地中海啊  真想通過西伯利亞鐵路去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那條線路似乎不到地中海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說為什麼你們也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也想來這裡吃吃看  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是絕佳的團隊合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒誇你  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是高山你不適合來這家店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那櫻井你就適合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵  你到底要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推薦各位試試主廚之選的午餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨  高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來札沼的OJT是在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  這套制服合身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯…就這點感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我是桐生鐵道高中的高二生  札沼麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙各位平時照顧高山君了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像娃娃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件制服真合適
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是鐵道高中學生的話  應該也是鐵道迷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的是電車的聲音和車站的發車音樂之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的音鐵對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵道高中的全都是些像高山這樣的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說也沒有高山君那麼奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  來份鯛魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠背正常  座位正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  可以坐下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點髒也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也這麼玩過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次一起在教室的時候還真被嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子正常  椅子正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然這樣叫起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指差呼喚確認是司機的基礎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然大家都爆笑起來了  但我覺得真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真地以列車司機為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以後會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得下去嗎  公安隊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  順其自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  那位櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種人  是不是更適合做公安的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢  有她在治安反而會變差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天到晚折騰來折騰去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知道她在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯田小姐不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋裡的柴油機在阻礙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是今天撿獲失物的統計表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要我來幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了  小海同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  嗯  這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後點擊這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點  點擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下落不明？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起製作來電鈴聲的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她昨天晚上開始就失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要到哪個車站去採集聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去以後  就再也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎麼打電話都沒有接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哪個車站呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是就那樣去旅行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那樣  至少會聯絡一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別見外了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫薰的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的就是從昨天開始所有的報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被捲入了在首都圈發生的事故的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會有一些消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都聽好了  對方是眾所周知的激進團體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公安機動隊  出動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是和以前一樣雞飛狗跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現今為止還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是至少有些線索的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請其他班的人幫忙怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再努力試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得幫助有困難的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們公安的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛公安隊的人出發了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公安的工作果然很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過那些人是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君也在做那樣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…有時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些東西希望你確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  等下再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個鈴聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是薰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個手機是在哪裡發現的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位小朋友撿到的  好像是在玩的時候發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母就送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說不知道在哪裡撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有照片什麼的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通話記錄呢  怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易得到的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要知道哪怕蛛絲馬跡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,語音文件呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰的話  也許留下了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的錄音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吵  過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海  還有其他的語音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這個的話  沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能從手機中留下的異味裡嗅出是哪個車站嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是喜歡鐵道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種程度的技能  趕緊學會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼  知道什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼眼前是大海啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國鐵鶴見線  海芝浦站
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站台面對京濱運河  是很罕見的車站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然語音文件裡只有一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能聽到拍打岸壁的波浪聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有制動試驗所發出的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只有折返的車站才有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能錄下電車和海浪聲音的國鐵車站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有海芝浦站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連波浪的聲音都聽得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為札沼的耳朵很靈敏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰是在這裡被捲入事件裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  在這周圍？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡除了公園  沒有許可是不能出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劫持著女性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能長時間乘坐電車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徹底搜尋這條線路沿線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新芝浦那邊也找下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人找到了  地點是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  不要久留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起來嗎？  扶穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種制服  是警察嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯了  是鐵道公安隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  為什麼會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們帶著薰快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為代理班長  我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說被逮捕的是違法販賣藥物的團體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰是碰巧到了交易現場  才被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷好像也不重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立功了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是只有誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  說不定喜歡上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是今天出院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只是以防萬一才住院的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說  沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  多虧了高山和其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝什麼的就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點變帥了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路平安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特急「舞者」號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由使用國鐵183系特急型電車運行的特急「天城」號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和使用153系急行型電車運行的急行「伊豆」號統合後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴隨新型直流特急型電車185系投入運用而誕生的特急列車
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  接下來請老老實實聽我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RAIL WARS!  第四話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許喜歡上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了  歡迎來到鹿島乃亞的舞台！
